      },
      "date": "2020-04-16 12:52:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nMy own testing on CentOS 7.7 gives the following results:\n* without this patch:\n# rpm -qpiR lustre-2*x86_64.rpm |grep selinux\nlibselinux\nlibselinux.so.1()(64bit)\n* with this patch:\n# rpm -qpiR lustre-2*x86_64.rpm |grep selinux\nlibselinux.so.1()(64bit)\n\nSo I guess this is fine to have the dependency on the .so file only.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
